  <brief_title>Riluzole in the Treatment of Bipolar Depression</brief_title>
  <official_title>Riluzole in the Treatment of Bipolar Depression: A Study of the Association Between Clinical Response and Change in Brain Glutamate Levels as Measured by Proton Magnetic Resonance Spectroscopy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
